              "Whatever the team needs... I'm a winner. So just trying to win."
            </p>
            <p class="quote-author">Tom Barlow</p>
            <p class="quote-role">On his playing philosophy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="quote-card fade-in">
            <p class="quote-text">
              "Tom's physical components and athleticism will be difficult for any defender
